### CCR-020 — Table Rebalance Saga
###
### 검증:
### - POST /tables/rebalance 응답에 saga_id, steps 포함
### - 207 Multi-Status (부분 성공) + 500 실패 시나리오
### - 각 step의 status: "pending" → "in_progress" → "completed" / "failed"

@host = http://localhost:8000
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}

### 12.1 POST /api/v1/tables/rebalance — 정상 (전체 성공)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tables/rebalance
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "flight_id": 1,
  "source_tables": [5, 6],
  "target_tables": [1, 2, 3]
}

# 예상 응답: 200 OK
# {
#   "saga_id": "rbl-01HVQK...",
#   "status": "completed",
#   "steps": [
#     { "step_id": 1, "action": "break_source_tables", "status": "completed" },
#     { "step_id": 2, "action": "reassign_players", "status": "completed" },
#     { "step_id": 3, "action": "notify_cc_instances", "status": "completed" }
#   ],
#   "players_moved": 18
# }

### 12.2 POST /api/v1/tables/rebalance — 부분 성공 (일부 테이블 가득 참)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/tables/rebalance
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "flight_id": 1,
  "source_tables": [10, 11, 12],
  "target_tables": [1, 2]
}

# 예상 응답: 207 Multi-Status
# {
#   "saga_id": "rbl-...",
#   "status": "partial",
#   "steps": [
#     { "step_id": 1, "status": "completed" },
#     { "step_id": 2, "status": "failed", "reason": "Target table 2 reached max_players" },
#     { "step_id": 3, "status": "skipped" }
#   ],
#   "players_moved": 7,
#   "players_pending": 11
# }

### 12.3 GET /api/v1/sagas/{saga_id} — saga 상태 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/sagas/rbl-01HVQK-test-saga-id
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 현재 saga 상태, step별 진행률, 롤백 가능 여부

### 12.4 POST /api/v1/sagas/{saga_id}/rollback — 부분 실패 후 롤백
POST {{host}}/api/v1/sagas/rbl-01HVQK-test-saga-id/rollback
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

# 예상: 완료된 step들을 역순으로 reverse
# 207 Multi-Status with rollback 결과
